
# Password-store

## Auto completion not working
* rm ~/.zcompdump*
* $ exec zsh

## Show stored passwords
* pass ls

## Copy password to clipboard
* pass -c something
* pass -c Folder/something

## Show password
* pass Folder/something
* pass something

## Add password
* pass insert Folder/something
* pass insert something

## Generate password
* pass generate Folder/something 15

## Remove password
* pass rm Folder/something

## Edit password
* pass edit something

## Git commands
* pass git status
* pass git push
